<link href="adcp.css" rel="stylesheet"><entry><xh5> be bothered about someone • bother oneself about someone</xh5><p> <i>be bothered about someone—</i>be concerned about smb.; worry about a person: I <u>am bothered about</u> Freda, she is out so late again.</p><p> <i>bother oneself about someone—</i>concern oneself with smb.; preoccupy oneself with a person: Please don’t <u>bother yourself about</u> my brother. I’ll take care of him.</p> </entry>
